animeDescription: Commercials and promotional videos commissioned by Iwaki Meisei University from Production I.G.Hashiru Shiki-henA girl runs through various seasons on campus.Digest-henA girl reminisces about activities on campus such as her friendships, studying, and joining a small percussion band.Ohai Alii: Kagayaku Hi no Tame niFor the new nursing school it shows what student life will be like at the nursing school by following a fictional freshman who joins the hula club.
